Package: milansql
Version: 5.7.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Mirwais Haidari <haidari9819@gmail.com>
Section: database
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://haidari9819-lang.github.io/milansql/
Description: Production-grade SQL database engine
 MilanSQL is a relational database engine built from scratch in C++17
 with zero external dependencies. It supports SQL-92 syntax, MVCC
 transactions, WAL crash recovery, full-text search, JSON, time-series,
 and a built-in HTTP/GraphQL API.
 .
 Features:
  - ACID transactions with MVCC
  - WAL crash recovery + Double-Write Buffer
  - MySQL and PostgreSQL wire protocol compatibility
  - Built-in HTTP REST and GraphQL APIs
  - Native C++17, zero external dependencies
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libstdc++6 (>= 9.0)
Recommends: systemd
Installed-Size: 4096
